’Ł@432be0a5c8435008e5f70bd61f18b1b22782072acbfcb006b1a50f73fbed14caŁāTitle: title: config use-colors
Path: Notes
Content:
Use this command instead of checking 
``$env.config.use_ansi_coloring``
 to properly handle the "auto" setting, including environment variables that influence its behavior.
